| [alerts.py L103-108](file:///c:/Users/caleb_8h6kswm/Documents/GitHub/threatmatrix-ai/backend/app/api/v1/alerts.py#L103-L108) | `body: AssignRequest` with `assignee_id: UUID` |

**Fix** — Change frontend to send body with correct field name:

```diff
