**Fix**: Refactor [useAlerts](file:///c:/Users/caleb_8h6kswm/Documents/GitHub/threatmatrix-ai/frontend/hooks/useAlerts.ts#58-146) to import and use `alertService` methods. Low priority — functional but inconsistent.

